	* src/gpm-manager.c: Add some debug text so we know the state.

	* src/gpm-dpms-x11.c (gpm_dpms_mode_from_string): Fix typo where
	"on" should be GPM_DPMS_MODE_ON rather than GPM_DPMS_MODE_OFF.

